{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-135-136-the-latest-report",
    "title": "Lesson 135: The latest report",
    "audioFilename": "135&136－The Latest Report.mp3",
    "duration": 120.268,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.62,
      "end": 2.64,
      "text": "Lesson 135.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第135课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 3.88,
      "end": 5.26,
      "text": "The Latest Report.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "最新消息。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 7.08,
      "end": 10.9,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 12.32,
      "end": 16.52,
      "text": "Is Karen Marsh going to retire, do you think?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你认为卡伦·马什会退休吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 18.77,
      "end": 22.15,
      "text": "Are you really going to retire, Miss Marsh?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "马什小姐，您真的准备退休吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 23.01,
      "end": 23.85,
      "text": "I may.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "有可能。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 24.57,
      "end": 27.01,
      "text": "I can't make up my mind.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我还拿不定主意。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 27.89,
      "end": 31.35,
      "text": "I will have to ask my future husband.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我得问问我未来的丈夫。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 32.03,
      "end": 35.47,
      "text": "He won't let me make another film.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他不会让我再拍电影了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 36.77,
      "end": 39.13,
      "text": "Your future husband, Miss Marsh?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您未来的丈夫，马什小姐？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 39.99,
      "end": 40.47,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "是的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 41.25,
      "end": 43.63,
      "text": "Let me introduce him to you.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "让我把他介绍给你们。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 44.29,
      "end": 46.45,
      "text": "His name is Carlos.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他叫卡洛斯。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 47.59,
      "end": 51.33,
      "text": "We're going to get married next week.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们下周就要结婚了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 53.13,
      "end": 53.83,
      "text": "Look, Liz.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "看，莉兹。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 54.71,
      "end": 58.33,
      "text": "Here's another report about Karen Marsh.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这里又有一篇关于卡伦·马什的报道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 58.33,
      "end": 59.87,
      "text": "Listen.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听着。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 61.53,
      "end": 62.09,
      "text": "Karen Marsh.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "卡伦·马什。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 62.89,
      "end": 63.49,
      "text": "The Latest.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "最新消息。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 64.75,
      "end": 72.71,
      "text": "At her London hotel today, Miss Marsh told reporters she might retire.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "今天，马什小姐在她下榻的伦敦酒店告诉记者，她可能会退休。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 73.95,
      "end": 77.31,
      "text": "She said she couldn't make up her mind.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她说她还拿不定主意。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 78.15,
      "end": 83.09,
      "text": "She said she would have to ask her future husband.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她说她得问问她未来的丈夫。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 83.09,
      "end": 90.95,
      "text": "She said her future husband would not let her make another film.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她说她未来的丈夫不会让她再拍电影。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "start": 92.05,
      "end": 100.85,
      "text": "Then she introduced us to Carlos and told us they would get married next week.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "随后她把卡洛斯介绍给我们，并告诉我们他们将在下周结婚。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s025",
      "start": 101.79,
      "end": 106.11,
      "text": "That sensational news, isn't it, Kate?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这可是条轰动性的新闻，对吧，凯特？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s026",
      "start": 106.11,
      "end": 109.13,
      "text": "It certainly is.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "的确是。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s027",
      "start": 109.91,
      "end": 112.75,
      "text": "He'll be her sixth husband.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他将是她的第六任丈夫。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
